  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to identify the major complications and their risk factors of
      elderly patients who had undergone Hemi-hip Arthroplasty.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      We retrospectively reviewed the medical records and reviewed the major complications and
      identify risk factors of elderly patients who had undergone Hemi-hip Arthroplasty for adults
      aged 60 years or older from January 2011 to December 2015.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
